                                                                            <h2 class="subtitulo">PRIVACY POLICY</h2>

<div class="section">
    1. GENERAL INFORMATION
</div>
<p>
    Using this ad JOBOMAS.COM (hereinafter "Jobomas") hereby informs users of its Internet portal "www.jobomas.com"
    (hereinafter "Users" and "Website") about its data protection policy.
</p>
<p>
    Please read this page carefully. IF YOU DO NOT ACCEPT THESE TERMS, DO NOT USE THIS WEBSITE. ANYONE WHO DOES NOT ACCEPT
    THESE TERMS AND CONDITIONS, WHICH ARE MANDATORY BINDING, YOU MUST NOT USE THE WEBSITE AND / OR SERVICES OFFERED ON
    THE WEBSITE.
</p>
<p>
    If the User uses the Website, is deemed to have fully and unreservedly accepted the Terms in effect at the time of
    access. Therefore, the User agrees to comply with all the provisions contained in these Terms and Conditions, under
    applicable laws, statutes, rules and regulations concerning the use of the Website . JOBOMASf the Website ( hereinafter
    " JOBOMAS " ) JOBOMAS reserves the right to amend this policy to adapt to new legislation or jurisprudence as well
    as industry practices. In such cases, JOBOMAS will announce on this page changes with reasonable notice before implementation.
</p>
<div class="section">
    2. WEBSITE REGISTRATION, DATA PROCESSING, UPLOADING CURRICULUM VITAE (CV)
</div>
<p>
    Jobomas collects personal data that the user voluntarily provides.
</p>
<p>
    <strong>2. a. Registration on the website</strong>
</p>
<p>
    When registering on the Website you will be asked to provide a JOBOMAS certain personal information (hereinafter "
    Personal Data") which shall include a valid email. Users can freely and voluntarily decide whether they wish to provide
    Personal Data to JOBOMAS that may be required or to be obtained from the users during the sign up on some of the
    services offered by JOBOMAS in the Portal or through the Portal.
</p>
<p>
    In addition to the terms and conditions that may be established later by any privacy policy on this website, you
    acknowledge and agree that JOBOMAS may disclose to third parties, on an anonymous basis, certain set of data contained
    in your application for registration.
</p>
<p>
    <strong>2.b. DATA PROCESSING</strong>
</p>
<p>
    Personal Data will be processed automatically and incorporated into the relevant files of personal data that will be
    owned and responsibility of JOBOMAS (hereinafter the " File"). For this purpose, JOBOMAS provides users with adequate
    technical resources so that, prior this they can access this notice on the Privacy Policy or get any other relevant
    information and give their consent to the ppropriate treatment of JOBOMAS Personal Data . Except in areas where
    otherwise noted, responses to questions about personal data are voluntary, without the lack of response implies a
    reduction in the quality or quantity of the services, unless otherwise indicated.
</p>
<p>
    The User guarantees that the personal data provided to JOBOMAS are truthful and is responsible for communicating any
    changes in them.
</p>
<p>
    JOBOMAS also provides user who has provided Personal Data ("Job Seeker") the possibility that, at any time, the Employment
    Applicant withdraws from JOBOMAS dabase.
</p>
<p>
    The collection and processing of Personal Data is for (i) the maintenance of the contractual relationship with JOBOMAS,
    (ii) the management and maintenance of job databases accessible by Employers to the effect that the employers can select,
    if any, potential candidates for job openings, (iii) the management, administration , provision, expansion and
    improvement of services in which the user decides to subscribe, register high or use the adaptation of these services
    to the preferences and tastes of the users, (iv) the study of the use of services by users, (v) the design of new services,
    (vi) sending updates of services, (vii) sending, by traditional and electronic means, of technical, operational and
    commercial information about products and services offered by or through JOBOMAS currently and in the future. The
    purpose of the collection and processing of personal data also includes sending survey forms, which the User is not
    obliged to answer.
</p>
<p>
    JOBOMAS may transfer the Personal Data to employers offering jobs, in order to enable them to study and identify potential
    candidates for vacant jobs in their company. In some cases, JOBOMAS shares Personal Data with third parties. When
    appropriate, considered that this shall have been requested by the user at the time of registration of his/her personal
    data , this will be duly advised to the Users in advance before the personal data are shared and the third party will
    be identified together with type of activities of the third party and the purpose behind the assignment. All companies
    related to JOBOMAS such as third parties that JOBOMAS shares information with can be located abroad.
</p>
<p>
    JOBOMAS has adopted the security levels of protection for personal data legally required, and has installed all the
    technical means and measures at its disposal to prevent the loss, misuse, alteration, unauthorized access and theft
    of personal data provided to JOBOMASl. Nevertheless, the user should be aware that Internet security measures are not
    impregnable.
</p>
<p>
    Certain services offered on the Website may contain conditions with specific provisions on the protection of personal data.
</p>
<p>
    JOBOMAS can and will, on occassion, send email advertisements regarding other websites that are owned, shareholders
    in or business partners of the company.
</p>
<p>
    In order to provide adequate service, Jobomas may share user data with various technological partners (clients or providers).
    Our partners include but are not limited to DigitalOcean (hosting service), Amazon (hosting and email delivery services),
    SendGrid (email delivery service), GoDaddy (hosting and domain services), and Google (advertising, web analytics,
    and additional services), among others. These providers do not collect personal information, which is only used to
    deliver marketing emails, understood as emails about the services acquired or the status of processes of those services
    offered by our web portal.
</p>
<p>
    Jobomas.com is owned by BECITHEW S.A. DE C.V. (29 Oriente 1609 Seccion Bandini, Puebla, México). By using this website
    you accept the terms and usage conditions in this document. Users may contact JOBOMAS whenever is needed via email
    <a href="mailto: info@jobomas.com">info@jobomas.com</a>
</p>
<p>
    <strong>2.c. Demand publishing service employment (the "Service").</strong>
</p>
<p>
    To use the service requires that the User is registered with the website.
</p>
<p>
    In case that JOBOMAS offers users the benefit of posting ads for free, they become aware and accept that JOBOMAS
    reserves the right to limit, in its sole discretion, the amount of available free monthly notices for registered uses,
    as well as the number of CVs that users may receive for free for their published ads. JOBOMAS can vary the amounts
    from time to time, thereby the user is not entitled to claim any.
</p>
